script.name: plugin.transactions.menu
script.sourceplaintext:
if $a.event == [MEvent.Start] gosub sub.BuildMenu return $input end return null
sub.BuildMenu: $is.station = [FALSE] if $a.obj -> exists if $a.obj -> is of class Station $is.station = [TRUE] end end $menu = create custom menu array
$column.count = 4 if $is.station $column.count = 3 else do if $a.obj -> exists $column.count = 3 end
$text.cols = array alloc: size=$column.count $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=4227 $text = create custom menu column string, position=0 length=105 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.cols[0] = $text $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=1104629 $text = create custom menu column string, position=105 length=100 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.cols[1] = $text $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=1104203 $text = create custom menu column string, position=220 length=200 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.cols[2] = $text if $column.count >= 4 $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=721 $text = create custom menu column string, position=-1 length=100 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.cols[3] = $text end add info line heading to menu: $menu, heading=$text.cols if $is.station $total.trans = $a.obj ->get total station money transactions else $total.trans = get total player money transactions end
if not $total.trans $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=689 add custom menu info line to array $menu: text=$read.text else $any.done = [FALSE] while $total.trans dec $total.trans =
if not $is.station $trans.obj = get player transaction object: id=$total.trans if $a.obj -> exists do if $a.obj != $trans.obj continue end end
$text.cols = array alloc: size=$column.count
if $is.station $text = $a.obj ->get station transaction time: id=$total.trans else $text = get player transaction time: id=$total.trans end $text = format date: $text ingame=[TRUE] $text = create custom menu column string, position=0 length=105 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$text $text.cols[0] = $text
if $is.station $money = $a.obj ->get station transaction money: id=$total.trans else $money = get player transaction money: id=$total.trans end $menu.col = [MenuColour.Normal] if is datatype[ $money ] == DATATYPE_ARRAY $billions = $money[0] $units = $money[1] $text = format large number pair as string: billions $billions, units $units, include separators [TRUE], use millions suffix for very large numbers [TRUE] do if $units < 0 OR $billions < 0 $menu.col = [MenuColour.Red] else do if $money < 0 $menu.col = [MenuColour.Red] $text = convert number $money to string end $text = create custom menu column string, position=105 length=100 right=[TRUE] colour=$menu.col text=$text $text.cols[1] = $text if $is.station $text = $a.obj ->get station transaction text: id=$total.trans else $text = get player transaction text: id=$total.trans end if $column.count == 3 $text = create custom menu column string, position=220 length=0 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$text else $text = create custom menu column string, position=220 length=490 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$text end $text.cols[2] = $text
if $column.count >= 4 skip if $trans.obj -> exists $trans.obj = '-' $text = create custom menu column string, position=-1 length=140 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$trans.obj $text.cols[3] = $text end
add custom menu info line to array $menu: text=$text.cols $any.done = [TRUE] end
if not $any.done $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=689 add custom menu info line to array $menu: text=$read.text end end
set menu option: $menu, icon=84 set menu option: $menu, no select lines=[TRUE]
$read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=1104630 if $is.station $player.name = $a.obj -> get name else $player.name = get player name end $input = create input: id='trans.menu', dynamic info menu=$menu, title=$read.text, description=$player.name, callback=null, update=2000ms, maxoptions=2 endsub return null
